(east_pacific_spprichness <- ggplot(data = shelf_areas[region == \East Pacific\], aes(x=latitude_start, y=change_spp_predicted_levin)) +
   geom_col(aes(fill=spp_change_pos_neg_levin), alpha = 0.5) +
